{
  "stem": "25114.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then came, uh-- We didn't get real passports.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were registered as refugees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not my sister, because my sister was the wife-- my older sister-- she was the wife of a citizen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because he was born there and he lived there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So she became automatically a citizen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was a refugee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, the KGB was calling me every three months, checking on me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at one stage, they told me to leave Nowogrodek, because it's too close to the borders-- to the other borders-- to the Lithuanian border, at this particular time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, where will I go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where I have got my sister, I've got my school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, oh, the Soviet Union is big.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You'll find a spot-- somewhere, by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't want to give me a passport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after a while the headmaster from my college interfered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said we're under his protection, and they are only children and they are only students with me and somebody else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave us an extension for another three months-- passport or document.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they annexed Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 1940, I think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They annexed-- Lithuania has become a Soviet republic-- all the three Baltic states.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it became irrelevant, because I was no longer close to the border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to be, I think, 140 kilometers from the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this became irrelevant, so I stayed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I actually enjoyed my stay there under the Soviet occupation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I was doing what I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was studying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was happy, I had-- I wasn't persecuted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Really, I only miss-- I had terrible homesick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had this experience as a-- from the month of bombing and starving and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
